file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: fruity
  version: 0.0.1
paths:
  "/":
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: desc
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/fruit_basket"
components:
  schemas:
    fruit_basket:
      title: fruit
      type: object
      required:
        - owner
      properties:
        owner:
          type: string
        fruits:
          items:
            # https://swagger.io/docs/specification/data-models/inheritance-and-polymorphism/
            anyOf:
              - $ref: '#/components/schemas/my_apple'
              - $ref: '#/components/schemas/my_banana'
            discriminator:
              propertyName: type
              mapping:
                banana: '#/components/schemas/my_banana'
                apple: '#/components/schemas/my_apple'
          type: array
    my_apple:
      title: apple
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
        kind:
          type: string
    my_banana:
      title: banana
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
        count:
          type: number
